<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: Feature to move Tabs all the way down in IE 9/10/11 ?]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=3380&amp;p=15773#p15773"><![CDATA[
It is not possible to move the tabs below the toolbars or the menu bar. The reason is that the tabs belong to the outer frame (the one that contains all pages) and the toolbars and menus are per page.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=2">Ivo</a> — Sun Nov 23, 2014 9:25 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
</entry>
